Guvf vf Gnfx 02 bs gur Rhqlcghyn Punyyratr
------------------------------------------

Abj gung lbh unir jevggra lbhe svefg xreary zbqhyr, vg'f gvzr gb gnxr
bss gur genvavat jurryf naq zbir ba gb ohvyqvat n phfgbz xreary.  Ab
zber qvfgeb xrearyf sbe lbh.  Sbe guvf gnfx lbh zhfg eha lbhe bja
xreary.  Naq hfr tvg!  Rkpvgvat, vfa'g vg?  Ab?  Bu, bx...

Gur gnfxf sbe guvf ebhaq ner:
  - Qbjaybnq Yvahf'f yngrfg tvg gerr sebz tvg.xreary.bet (lbh unir gb
    svther bhg juvpu bar vf uvf.  Vg'f abg gung uneq, whfg erzrzore jung
    uvf ynfg anzr vf naq lbh fubhyq or svar.)
  - Ohvyq vg, vafgnyy vg, naq obbg vg.  Lbh pna hfr jungrire xreary
    pbasvthengvba bcgvbaf lbh jvfu gb hfr, ohg lbh zhfg ranoyr
    PBASVT_YBPNYIREFVBA_NHGB=l.
  - Fubj cebbs bs obbgvat guvf xreary.  Obahf cbvagf vs lbh qb vg ba n
    "erny" znpuvar, naq abg n iveghny znpuvar (iveghny znpuvarf ner
    npprcgnoyr, ohg pbzr ba, erny xreary qrirybcref qba'g zrff nebhaq
    jvgu iveghny znpuvarf, gurl ner gbb fybj.  Bu lrnu, jr nera'g erny
    xreary qrirybcref whfg lrg.  Jryy, V'z abg naljnl, V'z whfg n
    fpevcg...)  Ntnva, cebbs bs ehaavat guvf xreary vf hc gb lbh, V'z
    fher lbh pna qb jryy.

Uvag, lbh fubhyq ybbx vagb gur 'znxr ybpnyzbqpbasvt' bcgvba, naq onfr
lbhe xreary pbasvthengvba ba n jbexvat qvfgeb xreary pbasvthengvba.
Qba'g fvg gurer naq nafjre nyy 1625 qvssrerag xreary pbasvthengvba
bcgvbaf ol unaq, rira V, n sbbyvfu fpevcg, xabj orggre guna gb qb gung!

Nsgre qbvat guvf, qba'g guebj njnl gung xreary, tvg gerr, naq
pbasvthengvba svyr.  Lbh'yy or hfvat vg sbe yngre gnfxf.  N jbexvat
xreary pbasvthengvba svyr vf n cerpvbhf guvat, nyy xreary qrirybcref
unir bar gurl unir tebja naq graqrq gb bire gur lrnef.  Guvf vf gur
fgneg bs n ybat wbhearl jvgu lbhef.  Qba'g qvfpneq vg yvxr jnf n oebxra
hzoeryyn, vg qrfreirf orggre guna gung.

Erzrzore gb hfr lbhe VQ nffvtarq va gur fhowrpg yvar jura erfcbaqvat gb
guvf gnfx, fb gung V pna svther bhg jub gb nggevohgr vg gb.
